				<headline type="str">Heat Advisory issued June 9 at 1:34PM CDT until June 9 at 8:00PM CDT by NWS Paducah KY</headline>
				<description type="str">* WHAT...Heat index values up to 105 expected.

* WHERE...Portions of southern Illinois, western Kentucky, and
southeast Missouri.

* WHEN...Until 8 PM CDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures and high humidity may cause heat
illnesses.</description>
				<instruction type="str">Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
